description:
#### New package name: __[bitvise-ssh-server](https://chocolatey.org/packages/bitvise-ssh-server)__

- - -

`winsshd.install` has been deprecated because of a software name change. In 2012, Bitvise released version 5.50 and renamed WinSSHD to "Bitvise SSH Server".

This package exists only for backward compatibility to provide a transitional dummy package for existing users and scripts which may still use this package ID.
summary: SSH Server provides secure remote login capabilities to Windows workstations and servers
author: Bitvise Limited
